  "title": "Project Manager | 0580",
  "description": "<ul><li>$5,500 - $6,500+ Car Allowance + Petrol Card + Season Parking</li><li>5 days - 8.30am to 5.30pm</li><li>Office Location: Ubi</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage end-to-end project delivery, ensuring scope, schedule, and budget compliance.</li><li>Establish effective communication channels with customers, internal teams, and third-party vendors.</li><li>Prepare and present clear status reports for different audiences, including executive management.</li><li>Develop and maintain realistic project schedules, considering dependencies and resources.</li><li>Proactively identify and resolve project issues.</li><li>Build strong relationships with customers and provide timely updates on initiatives and concerns.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or bachelor’s degree required.</li><li>Minimum 2 years in Project Management, preferably in construction projects</li><li>Experience in test planning, implementation, installation and ability to manage multiple complex projects simultaneously.</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
